  "description": "WinTuner GUI is a modern PowerShell-based graphical interface for managing Microsoft Intune Win32 apps via WinGet packages. Search WinGet packages, create .wtpackage files, and deploy them to Intune, with update checks for existing apps. Features include fuzzy app discovery, persistent settings, interactive M365 login, and a JSON settings store for end-to-end Intune app lifecycle management.",
